window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>This Publisher's Pack includes NEW DUET versions of Tribe Master books 1-3!</b></p> <p>Build a tribe. Kill monsters. Bed beautiful women. Become a master.</p> <p>After passing through a portal, test pilot Jack Hawthorne finds himself in the mysterious land of Agraria.</p> <p>It has everything in abundance–beautiful women, plentiful resources, and more than a few things that want to kill him.</p> <p>Now Jack must build his own tribe from the ground up if he wants to have a chance at surviving–and begin working towards the creation of his very own empire.</p>"; 
